snippet.textDisplay: The song is great! The composition is amazing! And Animes Roy is absolutely brilliant! But they would always be this good with or without Coke Studio. Needless to say, it is just a publicity stunt for a brand to feature a culture that it does not represent. For God's sake, they can't even use the right term in their description. Hajong is not just a 'tribe'. But of course, they will not use 'ethnic minority' because it will upset the status quo and harm their business. I am all for visibility and representation but without sharing the power and disrupting the polity, it is just tokenism. Talk about showing respect!

অলরেডি বার তিনেক শুনছি/দেখছি।
